{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"189c9a7fb2","title":"向党委进一言","origin":"《武汉大学右派言论汇编》（中共武汉大学社会主义思想教育办公室，1957.12）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a7d011f5a8","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"189c9a7fb2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"96efba516d","name":"夏名铠"},{"id":"c504f98253","name":"武汉大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"04e4df720d","type":"title","text":"向党委进一言","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"189c9a7fb2"},{"id":"c2c3ec60ed","type":"authors","text":"武汉大学夏名铠","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"189c9a7fb2"},{"id":"901e6605de","type":"subtitle","text":"（夏名铠：武汉大学图书馆学系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"189c9a7fb2"},{"id":"5da98450c5","type":"paragraph","text":"春雷终于响了，到处是一片“鸣”“放”的声音，这声音包含着人们对“三害”的巨大愤怒，迸发出多年来积郁在内心的呼声。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"189c9a7fb2"},{"id":"b1771853bf","type":"paragraph","text":"“武大”这几年来，一直为少数不学无术的张勃川、张希光、江橹、叶材植、王勇之辈所把持，他们别无能事，唯长于作威作福。他们披着共产党员的外衣，而灵魂深处却尽是自私自利，他们侮辱了“共产党员”这一光荣、豪迈的称号。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"189c9a7fb2"},{"id":"50b6546738","type":"paragraph","text":"“三害”在武大根深蒂固。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"189c9a7fb2"},{"id":"b610aff96c","type":"paragraph","text":"现在全校师、生，员、工都“鸣”起来了，为了澈底铲除“三害”，我们呼吁：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"189c9a7fb2"},{"id":"52ccef6d17","type":"paragraph","text":"1.让各民主党派领导人广泛向同学作报告。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"189c9a7fb2"},{"id":"942397e766","type":"paragraph","text":"2.让老教授广泛与同学接触，召开各系同学与教授集会。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"189c9a7fb2"},{"id":"09ae7dab9b","type":"paragraph","text":"3.希望党委向同学公布各校“鸣”“放”情况，鼓励群众斗志。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"189c9a7fb2"}],"page":{"id":"9a2466fb93","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"189c9a7fb2","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}